The evidence with the title 'The psychosocial needs of cancer patients - cancer care for the ... ' says Reflecting cancer's reach, 1 in 10 American households now includes a family member who has been diagnosed or treated for cancer within the past 5 years  ... 10 percent went without needed medical care , 30 percent delayed care , and 43 percent failed to fill needed prescriptions because of cost concerns ( Tu , 2004).
